app_standard.noteCN:
- 修改数据读取模式，调整targetSdk为23，旧版本需要卸载后再安装
- 更改部分Java Hook为Native Java Hook
- 现在区分x86,arm,all三个版本,部分模拟器优先使用arm会导致崩溃则需要下载x86版本
- 正常手机下载arm或all版本均可
app_standard.noteEN:
Modify the data reading mode and adjust targetSdk to 23. The old version needs to be uninstalled and then installed.
- Change some Java Hooks to Native Java Hook
- Now distinguish between x86, arm, all three versions, some emulators prefer to use arm If it causes a crash, you need to download the x86 version
- normal mobile phones can download the arm or all version
